<title>mn wyn yyjy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- mn wyn yyjy ạ̹blys wạ̉nt msyj ḥwạly
 kyf rạḥ ykẖṭfny mnk wạ̉nt ạlḥạrs ʿly
 1- kyf yqdr yw̉dẖyny wạldmgẖṭy̱ ạlạʿtạb
 kyf mmkn yfạjỷny wạlrwḥ shrạn ʿạlbạb
 2- kyf yqdr ywṣl ly wṣlybk qdạmy
 ạ̹nt slạḥy fy ḥrby wạ̉nt ʿny tḥạmy
 3- ạ̹ysẖ ʿndh ygẖryny sẖhwẗ qlby ʿndk
 kl mnạh ytwhny yḥrmny mn mjdk
 4- ạ̹nt ạlrạʿy ạlṣạlḥ tḥmy kl kẖrạfk
 bʿṣạtk tḥrshm wʿdwhm bykẖạfk</lyrics>
